      <title>美联储研究显示私营企业利润超过上市公司</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/private-companies-profits-outpace-public-firms-fed-study-shows</link>
      <description><![CDATA[旧金山联邦储备银行的研究人员表示，过去四十年来，上市公司的利润随着利率下降而下降，而私营公司的利润率却“大幅”上升。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-06-18/private-companies-profits-outpace-public-firms-fed-study-shows</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 18 Jun 2024 11:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
